csAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ftl1727955765003.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ftl1727955765003.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ftl1727955765003.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ftl1727955765003\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the maximum size of field names. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__section_wf4_y35_xcc\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS = field name size =\n\t\t\t\t\t</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldNameSize</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS = fldnmsize =\n\t\t\t\t\t</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldNameSize</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__topic_d31157e1_d31158e1_d31159e1_d31160e1_d31161e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218625e72\">Use </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__1\">Applies to</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__2\">Mnemonic</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__3\">Connector Syntax</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__1\">Informix connector</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__2\">INF</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"ftl1727955765003__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__p_d47684e1_d47685e1_d47686e1\">There are no restrictions on use.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__topic_d31162e1_d31163e1_d31164e1_d31165e1_d31166e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218625e124\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__p_d47690e1_d47691e1_d47692e1\">Use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">field name size</code> option to specify\n\t\t\t\tthe maximum size, in number of bytes, allowed for field names.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__p_d47693e1_d47694e1_d47695e1\">When specified, the connector truncates field names to the\n\t\t\t\tspecified size. The minimum size is <code class=\"ph codeph\">18</code> bytes and the maximum size\n\t\t\t\tis <code class=\"ph codeph\">128</code> bytes.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ftl1727955765003__pre_e5z_j35_xcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$Mnemonic_PARAMS = field name size =  32</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419931\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419931\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "field name size Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the maximum size of field names. USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = field name size = FieldNameSize USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = fldnmsize = FieldNameSize Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax Informix connector INF USYS$INF_PARAMS There are no restrictions on use. Description Use the field name size option to specify the maximum size, in number of bytes, allowed for field names. When specified, the connector truncates field names to the specified size. The minimum size is 18 bytes and the maximum size is 128 bytes. USYS$Mnemonic_PARAMS = field name size = 32 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}